## 8. Visual system (handoff)

Dark, minimal, precise. Spend boldness only on the cone; keep everything else quiet.

**Palette**
- Background deep cool-ink (near-black, slightly blue) · lifted panel surfaces · hairline borders.
- Text: primary ink, secondary muted, tertiary/labels dim.
- **Accent (interactive / hero lever): amber `#f5a524`** — used sparingly; a nod to the trading-terminal lineage this tool brings to retail.
- **Semantic only: downside coral `#ff6f6f`, upside teal `#4fd1c5`** — never decorative in the chart.
- **Asset-identity swatches** (allocation rows only): BTC amber, ETH periwinkle, SOL mint, Mid-cap violet, Microcap coral. Small and quiet — see the §5.2 colour guardrail.

**Type** (as built)
- Headings: **Space Grotesk** (clean, confident display).
- Body / UI: **Manrope**.
- All numbers: **JetBrains Mono** with **tabular figures** (`font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums`) so values don't change width as they update.
- Micro-labels: uppercase, wide tracking (~0.16em), ~10–11px, tertiary colour.

**Layout:** generous whitespace, hairline dividers, soft radii, no decorative gradients or shadows. Minimal directions live or die on spacing and type precision — get those exact. Theme driven by CSS custom properties so colours/fonts can be swapped live.

